Package uk.ac.manchester.cs.mekon.model.util

Provides utility classes that operate over the MEKON model.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CFrameIntersection
    Represents an intersection of CFrame objects.
    CFrameSubsumers
    Responsible for finding common subsumers for sets of concept-level frames.
    CHierarchy
    Light-weight representation of the hierarchical relationships in a CFrame-hierarchy, with frames being specified solely by the relevant CIdentity objects.
    CHierarchyBuilder
    Builder for a CHierarchy object.
    CNumberIntersection
    Represents an intersection of CNumber objects.
    CTypeValueIntersection<V extends CValue<?>>
    Represents an intersection of CValue objects of a specific type.
    CValueIntersection
    Represents an intersection of CValue objects.
    IFrameConverter<FTC,FC,SC>
    Abstract base class for classes responsible for converting IFrame/ISlot networks into other formats.
    ISlotListenerPropagator<L>
    Responsible for propagating a specified listener to dynamically selected ISlotValues objects that lie on recursive instance-level slot-frame-slot chains originating from one-or-more specified "seed-slots".
    ISlotUpdateListenerPropagator
    Propagator for KUpdateListeners.
    ISlotValuesListenerPropagator
    Propagator for KValuesListeners.
    IValuesUpdate
    Represents a slot-values-update operation.
    MFrameIntersection
    Represents an intersection of MFrame objects.
    MostExtremeCFrames
    Responsible for finding the most-specific or most-general members of a specified set of concept-level frames.
    MostExtremeCValues
    Responsible for finding the most-specific or most-general members of a specified set of concept-level values.
    MostGeneralCFrames
    Responsible for finding the most-general members of a specified set of concept-level frames.
    MostGeneralCValues
    Responsible for finding the most-general members of a specified set of concept-level values.
    MostSpecificCFrames
    Responsible for finding the most-specific members of a specified set of concept-level frames.
    MostSpecificCValues
    Responsible for finding the most-specific members of a specified set of concept-level values.
